| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4503 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1f7141d4-5fa8-5eaa-b9b2-0c4447d02490"
